{
  "stem": "18056.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that's-- we arrived then, of course, in Dachau [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when you were still at Auschwitz-- tell me a little bit more about that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What did you eat at Auschwitz?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What type of food?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At Auschwitz, they would give you, you know, the soldier-- for the military, they had these breads.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had-- to start off with, I think the first few days, they gave us-- like, two people a bread.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it was plenty to eat-- and good, fat, big-- not fat, but thick soup.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They fed you well in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And get up in the morning and do again the same thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is how it was, and until they would organize the groups to be sent out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you had the good group to really go out to work, like I did-- I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It could have been a-- a group that they said, we need-- we need 200 people to-- voom.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Instead of a left turn, they make a right turn, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "More or less no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would say, yeah, they need from 18 to 22.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was always in the-- in the group.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they-- when they-- when they-- when they were talking about age, I always looked a little older, because I told the guy, you know, when-- when they looked up and the muscles when you came into Auschwitz-- how old are you? 18. 18 is always the best age.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So I was able to kind of go through it because of that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they never really said-- they said, yeah, they're looking for a group that is gonna go to Munich, Berlin, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't know themselves what they were doing at this point.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
